(1,'《北京，北京》','    <p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">北京</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">北京</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在出发前</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">我</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">做了很多准备工作。而其中</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">遇见</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对我的帮忙非常大，我参考了许多篇游记规划的行程安排，制定出一份符合自己时间规划和兴趣所向的行程，在此非常感谢</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">遇见</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每当说起北京</span></span><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);text-underline:single\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></span></a><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，我第一反应就是长城，烤鸭，冰糖葫芦，故宫等等，但实际上，从未去过那里。所以总有去国家的首都走走的憧憬。于是拎起背包，就踏上了</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">北京</span></span><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);text-underline:single\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></span></a><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">之旅。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为了避免流水账般乏味的记载，我将北京</span></span><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);text-underline:single\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">之行分为</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个部分，分别是建筑篇，人文篇和胡同篇。原本人文应该包括建筑的，但我实在想不到别的词，而胡同又在建筑里面，但北京</span></span><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);text-underline:single\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">胡同别具一格，所以我专门挑出来作个详细一点的讨论。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一、建筑篇</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">作为一个国际化大都市，现代化的高楼当然在</span></span><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);text-underline:single\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></span></a><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">北京</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也是不少，比如</span></span><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63538.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);text-underline:single\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></span></a><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中关村，但除了高楼以外，北京</span></span><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);text-underline:single\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></span></a><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">还有另外两种建筑有着鲜明的特点，一是胡同，这留在第三部分说，二是黄色砖瓦红色城墙包着的宫殿。宫殿是明清时代留下的遗物，年代也不算久远，加上北方气候干燥，雨水侵蚀没低纬度地区厉害，所以外观保存得很好，只有个别被岁月侵蚀得斑驳，留给人感受到历史的沧桑感。与这个形成鲜明对比的是，城墙内绿树正欣欣向荣生机盎然，时间的沧桑和生命的兴荣造成强烈的对比，人总是很容易在这样的环境下有所触动。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">故宫是所有这些宫殿的代表者。这是一个很大的地方，以至于我</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">点左右进去的时候就开始觉得不妥，没有带什么吃的东西进去，但是这个地方不是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个小时就能走完。从进去到最后出来，大体花了将近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个小时。一路下来，走走停停，看着宏伟壮观的宫殿，想象以前是怎么在工具缺乏的情况下一点一点的将这庞大的工程完成，想象霸气威严的皇帝和底下低头大气都不敢喘一声的官员，想象宫殿里勾心斗角争权夺利的生活，眨眼时间就过去了。不过，我倒很喜欢大门底下阴影的地方，风很大，季节正好，人容易陶醉在此。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">另外，再补充几个景点照。包括师大图书馆，北大校门，清华园，北海</span></span><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10796.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);text-underline:single\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></span></a><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公园。建筑篇就到此为止。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人文篇</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"></span><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);text-underline:single\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></span></a><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">北京是个人杰地灵的地方，这里聚集了各式各样不同背景不同经历的人。其中，后海是这批人流较为集中的一个点，酒吧、湖水和驻唱的歌手，是这带的招牌魅力所在。北漂们怀揣着梦想，努力奋斗在这个密集的城市中，既励志又心酸。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"></span><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);text-underline:single\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></span></a><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">北京人还是挺热情的，至少我在困难的时候，他们还是非常乐意伸出援手。这位大爷看到我拍照，故意站久一点让我好拍；一群骚年在巷边烤着肉，也配合着做出手势来了个大合照。我想，如果要了解一个城市的人，一定要在这个地方住上一段时间，可惜我脚步匆匆，对于这个城市，我只是个过客。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>\r\n','2015-05-05',NULL,NULL,'5697225662@qq.com','images\\individual\\diary\\1(1).png'),
(2,'《西安你好，西安再见》','    <p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安你好，西安再见</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的感觉，四四方方的，城墙之内，你只要分得清南北就不会迷路，因为他就是</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大方</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">格套小方格，中轴线上就是钟楼。想迷路都难。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的感觉稳稳妥妥的。城墙顶上宽得就像省道，比有些国道都宽，他的基底更是宽厚，几朝连续的累积呈现出稳固的涵义。不用任何形容词，看到或者摸到，稳固的感觉会自然而生。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的感觉热虽热，但不是特有，全国都在热，要不，选洪水？台风？热一点算了。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的公交每站的距离远，站名路标不明显，感觉好客到故意收起路标，让你找不到离去的路，不忍你离去。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的的士还处于讲价的阶段，可能是外地人的原因？</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">只有一条地铁的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">已经感受到地铁的便捷了，在地铁上听本地人说的，恭喜啊，第二条</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份就要开通了。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的小吃太多了。停留在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天时间，西羊市的小吃面食还吃不完。建议多喝酸梅汤</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人蛮友善的，每天我都找点理由去问路，问些无关紧要的话，总会有答案可就是语速太快，多半听不懂</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的机场是环保低碳的，很少机场进去</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个小时还隐隐出汗的。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其实，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是一个适合</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自驾</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">游的城市，景点不远不近，都有停车场，加上公交系统提高空间很大，</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年之内还有机会来的话，我一定选择</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自驾</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">游</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西安</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">建议放缓速度，跟上本地人的节奏，你才能融入当地生活，你才能感受千年古都浸润在人们身上的印记。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">就像游城墙，不要仅仅坐个电瓶车转圈，租个自行车或者步行，一定要亲自丈量千年的高度、长度、厚度！把你的汗滴留在城墙之上，缓慢的抚摸城垛子、从敌楼往外看，呆呆的看上</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分钟</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分钟，你会感到你是一个有底气的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></span></p>\r\n','2015-05-07',NULL,NULL,'5697225662@qq.com','images\\individual\\diary\\2(1).png'),
(3,'《AMOY的身后，除了天空，皆是往事》','    <p><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\">AMOY的身后，除了天空，皆是往事</span></p><p style=\";text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\">&nbsp; 这是一次最美丽的邂逅，这是一次最甜蜜的际遇，这是一次让人无法释怀的暧昧。无论天高云淡，无论春暖花开，众里寻你，却让你我在茫茫人海中相遇。默然回首，只因你的回眸一笑，让我忘却了千年。</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">最厦门，最爱厦门的风情与浪漫</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">厦门的美是一个你不需要多说的地方。只要你有一双</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">“</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">慧眼</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">\"</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，用双脚去丈量，用赤子之心去感受，这里的美随处可见。厦门不是大家闺秀，她的美更不是浓妆艳抹、惊心动魄，我更愿意相信她是小家碧玉、邻家女孩，她的美正如羞答答的玫瑰一般，在静悄悄的绽放，这种美相信连</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">“</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">神</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">\"</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">都会动凡心。厦门是个全城热恋的城市，厦门的四季都是恋爱的季节。这里的风情和浪漫有花为媒，海为证，在周遭的小岛上都会杳杳传来爱的罗曼史。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">半城花语满城香，厦城无处不飞花。空气中到处弥漫着温暖香甜的味道，沁人心脾。明艳动人的三角梅、洁白芬芳的白玉兰，静静地开放着，每个行人都放慢了脚步，不忍心惊醒她。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">传说中中国最美丽的大学</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">——</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">厦门大学，这里集美貌与智慧于一体，可以说是厦门的掌上明珠，是万千学子魂牵梦萦的象牙塔。这里风月无边，芳草萋萋，落梅如雪，好一副诗情画意。偌大的花园中，不时有莘莘学子走走停停，不知是在驻足沉思，还是在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">“</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">想入非非</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">\"</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">“</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自强不息，止于至善</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">\"</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是儒家几千年来的终极追求，无意中让这个花园平添了一份阳刚，在美丽的外表下潜藏着为实现理想而积蓄的力量。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">“</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">跨过时空的阻隔，我们终于相遇</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">\"</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">来到厦门</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，你必须承认浪漫是渗透在每个人的血液里的。这里有一座充满风情的岛屿</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">——</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">鼓浪屿</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，这是一片用音乐滋养的土地，好像大自然里每一个生物都会歌唱。音乐就是鼓浪屿居民的集体记忆，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">10000</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多人的原住民却藏有超过</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">500</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">架钢琴，在这里，音乐不是高不可攀的阳春白雪，她就像锅碗瓢盆一样飞入寻常百姓家。在这里，每个人都是一个美妙的音符，串联成完美的五线谱，在大自然这个指挥家的指挥下，时而高亢嘹亮，时而平缓柔和，演奏着一幕幕华彩乐章。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"></span></p><p style=\";text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: auto 0px;\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">最厦门，最爱厦门的单纯与静谧</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\">&nbsp; 如果美丽、风情和浪漫是厦门</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">最引人入胜的一面，那么，单纯和静谧无疑是厦门最具内涵的一面。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">尽管大量游客闻其名潮水般涌入，异域文化不断冲击，但当地人的淳朴、热情、好客未曾改变，显得特别得可贵。问路时，当地人知无不言、不厌其烦的指引，小吃店主一次次慷慨赠送小吃供游客品尝，在街边品尝海鲜时，摊主一遍遍关切询问是否符合口味，不一而足，其实，单纯也是一种美。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">鼓浪屿的乡间宁静而安详，别具一格的南洋建筑静坐一隅，栉风沐雨，饱经沧桑，依然岿然不动，就像是一部精装的线装书，述说着过往的沧海与桑田。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">古彦道：</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">“</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一年来南普，三年免受苦</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">\"</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。往昔香烟缭绕的盛况佛乡</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\">——</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">南普陀，虽然岁月如流，人世沧桑，如今香火鼎盛，千年不败。身边穿行如梭的善男信女恪守虔诚，只为那心中神圣的理想和祝愿。这座千年古刹虽历经风雨，风貌依旧。怪石嶙峋，树影婆娑，溪水潺潺，满山滴翠，置身其中，心静如水。看着如心状般的菩提树，就像一位得道高僧，修炼于尘世，正果于深山，一阵微风吹来，一片片菩提叶从树梢上缓缓落下，我想那一定是佛祖为世人许下的祝福。一泓清清的泉水在微微荡漾，诉说着千年古刹的神秘与悠远。绝壁千仞涓滴成溪蜿蜒树间汇入大河的禅趣，在冥冥中，这就是一次机缘。此刻，我似乎明白那荒山中僧徒苦苦修行的意义，也好像体会到佛祖在滚滚红尘的拈花一笑。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:13px\"></span></p>\r\n','2015-06-05',NULL,NULL,'1094290936@qq.com','images\\individual\\diary\\3(1).png'),
(4,'《拉萨，明年我再回去看你》','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨，明年我再回去看你</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，很多人向往的地方，甚至是一生的旅行梦想地，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能带给我们什么呢？大概每个人都会从这里得到或多或少的东西。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">宗教在这里总是头等的大事，很多不信佛教的人来到</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也会被大大小小的寺院氛围所影响，尤其在大昭寺，你会不知不觉地跟着转经的大部队开始围着大昭寺转；从而对大昭寺肃然起敬，门口永远都有那么多磕长头和拍照的人。当然我们不能不到布达拉宫，毕竟那里是</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西藏</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">最漂亮的建筑，也是世界上绝无仅有的宫殿建筑。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">河的自然风光也会让你流连忘返，即使在冬天的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，河里面也会有成群的野鸭和水鸟，远处的雪山更映衬出河谷的俊美。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">哲蚌寺每年藏历新年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">晒大佛</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，会是很多游客不能错过的幸事，那天凌晨就要早早起来奔向哲蚌寺，在山上选个最佳的位置，如果去晚了就很难找到一个好位置了。其实，在冬天，哲蚌寺才最有韵味，很多牧区的藏族人会赶往</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">来朝拜三大寺庙，这时候没有那么多的游客，清晨，随着朝拜的藏人拾级而上，你大概有些了不一样的感受。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">色拉寺的辩经最有名，辩经的场面很是吸引人，都在下午进行，可惜我听不懂，只好像看舞台剧般的欣赏他们丰富的面部表情。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">另外，我还随着住寺的喇嘛听了一下他们的讲经课，当然是一头雾水，除了感受气氛以外，什么都听不懂。一般一个老师会给十几个学生讲课，时间约是两个小时，下午的阳光洒进不大的房间，学生们席地而坐，带上一壶酥油茶，边喝茶边聆听佛教讲义。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的乐子还有更多可说的，我却不能一一尽述，倒是在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">还有一件事，大概有在旁的城市是无法体验的乐趣，晒太阳，喝甜茶。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">特别就在于这里是海拔</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多米的城市；这里的原著民是藏族；这里的食物和世界其它地方有着很多的不同；这里的太阳一年四季都那么耀眼和炙热；这里的自然条件属于恶劣中最好的那种。。。有太多的不同，所以有了</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">西藏</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，有了</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有很多甜茶馆，尤其在八廓街一带，也就是围绕着大昭寺，虽然都叫甜茶馆，却是什么人进什么甜茶馆。有几十块钱一壶的甜茶，例如玛吉阿米、雪域餐厅，因为这些地方大都是游客去，环境优越，餐具干净。也有藏族人去的八廓甜茶馆，一壶甜茶只要</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">块钱，而一碗地道的藏面小碗只要</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">块，前提是如果你不嫌脏的话，这里要比那些窗明几净的甜茶馆更有味道，昏暗的灯光，拥挤的小桌，混杂着浓浓的各种味道，捎带手，保不齐你就邂逅几位地道的藏族小伙、姑娘。我就是在这里认识的藏族姑娘，达珍和拉姆。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不过要论起来晒太阳最舒服的茶馆，应该算是大昭寺广场前的刚吉茶馆，这里的从早上可以一直晒到夕</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阳西</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下，只要你有时间，你就可以一天赖在这里，就连午饭这里的味道和价格也都那么可人心，不过因为太阳太好了，甜茶也就应该</span>15<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">块一壶了。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: auto 0px;\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的太阳是如此的耀眼和灼热，即便是冬天，只要你坐在太阳底下，你一会儿就要把厚厚羽绒服脱掉，如果生猛点的，准保耍单儿穿个背心跟那显混（这种人以鬼子居多）。但是你如果转到阴影里，必须马上穿上外套，不然，就勤着感冒吧。这种时刻你就会明白藏族人的藏袍有多地道了。热了，一突撸，露出上半身，冷了，伸</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">进袖子就穿上了。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在这里你不可能不爱上晒太阳，喝甜茶，因为太惬意了，太舒服了，大概有个原因，就是因为海拔高的缘故，人不可能急匆匆的，同时，这里也的确没有太多事可干，比起瞎踅摸，懒散的坐在太阳下，享受丝丝的奶茶香味，才是真正的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生活。</span></span></p>\r\n','2015-07-05',NULL,NULL,'243651908@qq.com','images\\individual\\diary\\4(1).png'),
(5,'《魅力广州》','    <p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">魅力广州</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">此行来</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">广州</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">最重要的事情是拜黄大仙。小时候爸爸从</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">香港</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">给我带回来一个黄大仙的钥匙扣，每逢大事对着其拜一拜，都逢凶化吉。后来钥匙扣丢了。没有办法在大考之前我下载了黄大仙的照片设为手机壁纸对着其每天拜，说来也怪我很惊险的以压线的最低分考上可</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">蚌埠</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">医学院。妈妈拜的安徽</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">九华山</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，奶奶拜的观音</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">菩萨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，我都要一</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一感激他们。传说中的黄大仙有求必应，所以特意来</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">广州</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">还愿，至于</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">香港</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的黄大仙祠以后再去。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">黄大仙祠里面的环境挺好的，有好多神明的照片就不敢发了。留着在家慢慢拜。好多香炉还有爬满乌龟的水池，相信去的人不仅去看景色，重要的是给众大仙烧香。上面卖东西的阿姨人超级好的，她不会说普通话，幸好我的粤语略懂，跟她交流还是可以的。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">求了几件物品回去后。我们坐地铁去了上下九步行街。这条街不仅有美食还有超级便宜的衣服。终于吃到正宗的银记肠粉和双皮奶，衣服牛仔都是几块钱至</span>20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">块钱。还可以买手信回家带给朋友。享受这种感觉，突然下场大雨，然后撑着伞逛街</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步行街很长，有时间一定要细逛才过瘾，然后我们坐着旅游巴士去了珠江。有情调的人可以花钱坐豪华船夜游珠江，看看小蛮腰也就是</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">广州</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电视塔，第一高建筑奥。至于住宿，本来定在火车总站越秀公园旁边的七天酒店的，结果我堂堂银卡会员居然那么贵，所以索性住在七天下面的私人酒店叫什么宇通大酒店。里面不太干净，更可怕的是全部都住的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">非洲印度</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人各种黑人，只有我一个</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人。晚上下楼的时候发现整条街不管是商店还是餐馆全部都是老外居然没有</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人。顿时觉得自己好渺小，这是我的国家我的领土啊。后来看到牌子才知道原来住的地方在留学生管理中心，顿时松了一口气，终于看到了一个</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人感到爆亲切。第二天出发</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">回武汉</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，再见了</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">广州</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">我爱你。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>\r\n','2015-08-05',NULL,NULL,'243651908@qq.com','images\\individual\\diary\\5(1).png'),
(6,'《我爱这哭不出来的浪漫》','            <span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">我爱这哭不出来的浪漫</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">我喜欢一个人在一个陌生的地方闲荡，感受一下当地的风土人情，可以的话呆下来和本地人聊聊天什么的。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">而在这之前对</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">重庆</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的印象，除了红歌，不外乎就是火锅</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和美</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">女。。但我更喜欢去比较老旧的地方走走。。始终觉得要了解一个地域的风情，最合适的地方就是市井，还有老式的交通工具。。。由于时间的关系，怪蜀黍只去了十八梯和瓷器口，搭巴士轻轨转了一大圈，不叫游玩，只是静静地感受了一下这个城市。。。我不反对时代的进步，而且现实生活中有些地方真的需要通过改造来改善大伙的生活环境，但真的希望各位领导在带领咱们大步前进的时候也要注意保留逝去时代的印记。。我不知道这里有多少孩子是在小巷中吃喝拉撒长大的，有多少人家里的老人还生活在这种小巷子中。。我想过不了多久十八梯的房子会全部被推倒，到时又会有多少人回去缅怀在这里发生的点点滴滴。。有水有山，城市森林，森林</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">重庆</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，有机会我还会再来！</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对渡轮和索道无比崇拜的我，一定会去的长江索道。。怪蜀黍成长的地方没有这些富有生活气息的交通工具，悲哀啊。。。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中间有一天住川美旁边，进去逛了一逛。。。顿时感觉整个人充满了文艺气息。。。。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">瓷器口，但感觉游人太多，还好有个小妹妹带我逛了些清静的街道。。。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(252,242,220)\"></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">The&nbsp;End...</span></p></span></span>\r\n','2015-09-05',NULL,NULL,'243651908@qq.com','images\\individual\\diary\\6(1).png');

